36
00:01:50,041 --> 00:01:52,875
[ISUZU]
Here, grab this candy bar.

37
00:01:52,958 --> 00:01:54,250
[SUBARU gasps]

38
00:01:54,333 --> 00:01:55,666
[panting]

39
00:01:55,750 --> 00:01:57,916
[PAC2-AR]
It worked! He's back!

40
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,458
[ISUZU]
Just as I suspected.

41
00:01:59,541 --> 00:02:01,666
He's got a cockpit addiction.

42
00:02:01,750 --> 00:02:04,833
Losing the Durandal so
suddenly tore him up.

43
