44
00:02:06,750 --> 00:02:07,958
[PAC2-AR]
Make sure you keep breathing.

45
00:02:08,041 --> 00:02:09,375
[ISUZU]
Hey, Pecker.

46
00:02:09,458 --> 00:02:11,666
