of the sun like, now.

47
00:02:11,750 --> 00:02:13,000
Think you can swing that?

48
00:02:13,083 --> 00:02:14,916
[PAC2-AR] Think you can
maybe get my name right?

49
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:17,041
Subaru, wait! Don't leave!

50
00:02:21,416 --> 00:02:22,416
