51
00:02:22,500 --> 00:02:25,208
Where are you going? [growls]

52
00:02:25,291 --> 00:02:26,333
Get in, Pecker.

53
00:02:26,416 --> 00:02:28,708
[PAC2-AR]
PAC2-AR! It's not that hard!

54
00:02:30,041 --> 00:02:31,458
[ISUZU]
There's the cab.

55
00:02:36,708 --> 00:02:38,333
[ISUZU]
Gotcha!

56
