119
00:05:13,833 --> 00:05:16,541
These guys must be
really bored out here.

120
00:05:16,625 --> 00:05:18,916
Not gonna lie. I kinda
want one of everything.

121
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:20,541
Samers.

122
00:05:22,208 --> 00:05:24,541
I'm pretty sure we found
all the <i>Tiramisu</i> merch.

123
00:05:24,625 --> 00:05:26,833
[PAC2-AR]
There's so much of it!

124
00:05:26,916 --> 00:05:28,833
[ISUZU] Almost all of
it's edible. Weird.

125
00:05:28,916 --> 00:05:30,291
[PAC2-AR]
I get to be a plushie!

126
00:05:30,375 --> 00:05:32,666
I'm so soft, I can't help
feelin' myself!

127
00:05:32,750 --> 00:05:34,875
[SUBARU]
Rude! Where's my merch?

128
00:05:34,958 --> 00:05:36,000
After all I've done for them,

129
00:05:36,083 --> 00:05:37,916
don't I deserve
an action figure?

130
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:40,375
[ISUZU]
