140
00:06:02,041 --> 00:06:05,375
Do those jerks just think the
Earth keeps itself safe or what?

141
00:06:05,458 --> 00:06:07,125
I have a beautiful chin,
you sons of bitches!

142
00:06:07,208 --> 00:06:10,166
Hey! It's not the toy's fault!

143
00:06:10,250 --> 00:06:13,125
[PAC2-AR] You're not Mr. Subaru
and you never will be!

144
00:06:13,208 --> 00:06:14,833
[groans]

145
00:06:14,916 --> 00:06:16,583
